summary: Comprehensive frontend testing of VoyCargo refactored website completed successfully. All core features working including hero section, navigation, pricing with region tabs, quote form with calculation, WhatsApp integration, and mobile responsiveness.

Services section displays 4 service cards correctly
Region tab switching updates pricing data dynamically
Quote form validation requires weight input
Quote form calculation displays results correctly
WhatsApp integration with 4 working links and correct phone number
Testimonials section displays 3 testimonials with 5-star ratings
Footer renders with logo, links, contact, and flags
Mobile responsive design - menu toggle works, desktop nav hides
Smooth scroll navigation to all sections
Page performance - all images loaded, CSS/JS working
